snippet.title: Nazo Puyo: Arle no Roux (Game Gear) - Gameplay
snippet.description: The third installment of the Game Gear Nazo Puyo games.  It's essentially a port of the SNES game Super Nazo Puyo, focusing on the Arle half of the game, and switching up the puzzles.
